<p><hi rend='Bold'><foreign>VIZCAY</foreign>TIK BIZKAIRA</hi></p>
<p><mentioned>R. M. AZKUETAR ABADIAK</mentioned></p>
<p><mentioned>BEREN AITA ZANAN GOMUTAGARRITZAT</mentioned></p>
<p><mentioned>IRU ATALETAN</mentioned></p>
<p><mentioned>EGI&Ntilde;IKO</mentioned></p>
<p><mentioned>EREZI - IRAUTSIJA</mentioned></p>
<p><mentioned>BILBON</mentioned></p>
<p><mentioned>1895 GARREN URTIAN</mentioned></p>
<p><mentioned>Astuitar J.-n moldagintzan</mentioned></p>
<p><mentioned>Jaubeduna da</mentioned></p>
